languages.text: "Вы изучили тысячи книг и желаете знать все обо всем — меня восхищают ваш ум и любознательность".

traits.locale_text: "Вы изучили тысячи книг и желаете знаеть все обо всем — меня восхищают ваш ум и любознательность".

languages.text: "You have studied thousands of books. You wish to learn everything there is to learn — and I am dazzled by your keen mind and curiosity."

languages.text: “你博览群书，想要探索世间的一切知识。我迷恋你敏锐的头脑、炽热的好奇。”
languages.original_text: "You have studied thousands of books. You wish to learn everything there is to learn — and I am dazzled by your keen mind and curiosity."

traits.locale_text: “你博览群书，想要探索世间的一切知识。我迷恋你敏锐的头脑、炽热的好奇。”

languages.text: "Ihr habt tausende von Büchern studiert. Ihr wollt alles lernen, was es zu lernen gibt — und ich bin hypnotisiert von Eurem scharfen Verstand und Eurer Neugier."
languages.original_text: "You have studied thousands of books. You wish to learn everything there is to learn — and I am dazzled by your keen mind and curiosity."

traits.locale_text: "Ihr habt tausende von Büchern studiert. Ihr wollt alles lernen, was es zu lernen gibt — und ich bin hypnotisiert von Eurem scharfen Verstand und Eurer Neugier."

languages.text: « Vous avez étudié des milliers de livres. Vous voulez apprendre tout ce qu'il y a à savoir, et je suis {mf|ébloui|éblouie} par votre curiosité et votre esprit aiguisé. »
languages.original_text: "You have studied thousands of books. You wish to learn everything there is to learn — and I am dazzled by your keen mind and curiosity."

traits.locale_text: « Vous avez étudié des milliers de livres. Vous voulez apprendre tout ce qu'il y a à savoir, et je suis {mf|ébloui|éblouie} par votre curiosité et votre esprit aiguisé. »

languages.text: «Ha leído miles de libros. Quiere aprender todo lo habido por aprender. Me encandila la agudeza de su mente y su curiosidad».
languages.original_text: "You have studied thousands of books. You wish to learn everything there is to learn — and I am dazzled by your keen mind and curiosity."

traits.locale_text: «Ha leído miles de libros. Quiere aprender todo lo habido por aprender. Me encandila la agudeza de su mente y su curiosidad».

languages.text: 「あなたは何千もの本を読み、学んできた。あなたはそこにあるものすべてを学び取ることを望んでいる…その熱心さと好奇心には驚嘆しかない」

languages.text: "Okuduğun kitapların sayısı binleri aşmış. Öğrenilecek ne varsa öğrenmenin peşindesin. Keskin zekânla, merakınla başımı döndürüyorsun."
languages.original_text: "You have studied thousands of books. You wish to learn everything there is to learn — and I am dazzled by your keen mind and curiosity."
